description: An illustration of a dollhouse consisting of four rooms in a 2-by-2 configuration; the dollhouse lacks a back wall so that the interior can be accessed. The top left room has a tall vaulted ceiling and a rectangular prism-shaped object in the center; the top right room has a long pink rectangle painted onto the floor; the bottom left room has a thin rectangular prism-shaped object against the left wall and a pink octagon painted onto the floor; and the bottom right corner has a long L-shaped model counter against the back and right wall.
